<li>&#10004; Multi-turn conversation with context management</li>
<li>&#10004; Error handling with retry and exponential backoff</li>
<li>&#10004; Response caching for performance optimization</li>
<li>&#10004; User feedback mechanism (thumbs up/down)</li>
<li>&#10004; Enhanced UI with chat thread, feedback buttons, cache indicator</li>
<li>&#10004; Deployed to Vercel production</li>
<li>&#10004; Pushed to GitHub</li>
</ul>
